
NginX

What is it?
    - It is an open-source web server written in C
    - It can also be used as a reverse proxy & load balancer 


Current & Desired Architecture

Layer 4 & Layer 7 Proxying 

Example
    - NginX as a Web Server, Layer7 and Layer 4 Proxy 
    - Enable HTTPS, TLS 1.3 & HTTP/2 on NginX 

